OL,4,GBBC Northern Ireland's main local news
OL,5,Gprogramme, BBC Newsline, launched a new
OL,6,Glook today.
OL,8,FToday's breakfast and lunchtime
OL,9,Fprogrammes were broadcast from the
OL,10,Ftemporary set in Studio 1 at
OL,11,FBroadcasting House in Belfast. The
OL,12,Ftemporary facility has been in use
OL,13,Fsince August, whilst construction and
OL,14,Ftechnical testing of the new set-up in
OL,15,FStudio B was in progress.
OL,17,FThe updated set in Studio B was
OL,18,Frevealed on air at 6.30pm. It's based
OL,19,Fon the design and technology used in
OL,20,FStudio B at New Broadcasting House in
OL,21,FLondon.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
OL,22,                                   G1/3
