OL,4,FThe Belfast set-up includes a desk, a
OL,5,Fmonolith video tower and a large
OL,6,Frectangular videowall.
OL,8,FStudio B retains its green screen
OL,9,Ffacility which adjoins the main
OL,10,Fphysical set. A virtual set is used for
OL,11,Fthe sports segment within the 6.30pm
OL,12,Fweekday programme.
OL,14,FThe weather presenter utilises a large
OL,15,Fsection of the main videowall for the
OL,16,Fweather forecast at the end of the
OL,17,F6.30pm programme. All other weather
OL,18,Felements (including during the 6.30pm
OL,19,Fopening headlines) are based in the
OL,20,Fsmall Studio C green screen facility.
OL,3,CBBC Newsline launches new look
